    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331100/extras/36e0e8e2866cd91bd8cf427e22485829.poster.avif?t=1724241531\" width=300 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331100/extras/36e0e8e2866cd91bd8cf427e22485829.webm?t=1724241531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331100/extras/36e0e8e2866cd91bd8cf427e22485829.mp4?t=1724241531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>序章和EA版的区别：<br>序章：解锁30个战役关卡<br>EA版：解锁60个战役关卡，开放自定义地图和挑战功能<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >30个特色战役关卡，多种通关方式</h2>游戏拥有30个战役关卡，每个关卡都经过精心设计，面对新的建筑、新的兵种以及不同的战况，该如何选择你的策略呢？每个关卡都有不一样的通关方式，只要把城堡全部占领就行，尽情发挥你的脑洞吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331100/extras/7241fe50a360dd48597ec4f0fa83c87d.poster.avif?t=1724241531\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331100/extras/7241fe50a360dd48597ec4f0fa83c87d.webm?t=1724241531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331100/extras/7241fe50a360dd48597ec4f0fa83c87d.mp4?t=1724241531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁新建筑和新兵种，策略搭配多元化</h2>随着战役关卡推进，将会不断解锁新建筑和新兵种，游戏共有13种建筑，6种特色鲜明的兵种，根据每个关卡提供的不同地形和兵种进行搭配，让你的策略不止一种。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331100/extras/1a348cdeeb610d53ca2fc1dead2c4a4f.poster.avif?t=1724241531\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331100/extras/1a348cdeeb610d53ca2fc1dead2c4a4f.webm?t=1724241531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331100/extras/1a348cdeeb610d53ca2fc1dead2c4a4f.mp4?t=1724241531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1000+张玩家自定义地图，甚至可以上手DIY地图</h2>游戏已开放地图编辑器系统，你可以随意游玩由玩家自定义的1000+张创意地图战役，收藏、评论或分享你喜爱的地图，同样也可以自己编辑地图关卡，并上传分享给其他玩家。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331100/extras/c7ad469ebcd696b6daf06b5549158b5a.poster.avif?t=1724241531\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331100/extras/c7ad469ebcd696b6daf06b5549158b5a.webm?t=1724241531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331100/extras/c7ad469ebcd696b6daf06b5549158b5a.mp4?t=1724241531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
